{
  "keyword": "DSPOBJD",
  "description": "Display Object Description (DSPOBJD)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "OBJ",
      "description": "Object",
      "help": "Object (OBJ)\n\nSpecifies which objects in the library or libraries are to have their object attributes shown. If library (qualifier 2) is not specified, *LIBL is assumed, and all libraries in the library list for the current thread are searched for the objects.\n\nObjects in a library for which you do not have some authority other than *EXCLUDE authority are not shown unless a value of *NAME is specified for the Detail (DETAIL) parameter.\n\nNote: When *NAME is specified, authority to the object is not required.\n\nThis parameter can be specified as a single value or as a list of one or two qualifiers.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nSingle values\n\nQualifier 1: Object\n\nQualifier 2: Library\n\nUser libraries are all libraries with names that do not begin with the letter Q except for the following:\n\nAlthough the following libraries with names that begin with the letter Q are provided by IBM, they typically contain user data that changes frequently. Therefore, these libraries are also considered user libraries:",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": true,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "singleValues": [
        "*ALLUSR",
        "*IBM"
      ],
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *USRLIBL, *CURLIB, *ALL, *ALLUSR",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*LIBL",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "*LIBL"
        },
        {
          "name": "OBJ",
          "description": "Object",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *ALL",
